{
  "circuit": {
    "description": "Tier-2 gate: current-controlled switch (ngspice CSW / W element). Control branch: Vctrl(5V)->Rctrl(50ohm)->Vsense(0V sense). Control current = 0.1A > pullInI(0.05A) => switch closed. Switched path: Vin(5V)->CSW.A1, CSW.B1->Rload(1k)->gnd. Only CSW + verified DcVsrc/R.",
